eration with low heat build-up","href":null}],"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81a7-af67-e8c87e978ee7","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-814c-b08a-ecac35715a01"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"image","image":{"caption":[],"type":"external","external":{"url":"https://maxamtire.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MS412-stone-ejector-close-up.png"}},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8189-9321-e03ead1d105d","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-814c-b08a-ecac35715a01"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"While the MS402 is suitable for some mine sites and applications that demand extra-long tread life, MAXAM Mining Group (MMG) has recorded that the MS412 delivers the highest TMPH of all E4 tires*. Taking the feedback from customers that the MS402 may spin and experience separation in roads that are not as well-maintained, our engineers created the MS412 pattern with specific features in mind to help eliminate some of the shortcomings the MS402 may encounter.  ","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"While the MS402 is suitable for some mine sites and applications that demand extra-long tread life, MAXAM Mining Group (MMG) has recorded that the MS412 delivers the highest TMPH of all E4 tires*. Taking the feedback from customers that the MS402 may spin and experience separation in roads that are not as well-maintained, our engineers created the MS412 pattern with specific features in mind to help eliminate some of the shortcomings the MS402 may encounter.  ","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-817f-a11a-ed9327582170","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-814c-b08a-ecac35715a01"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"*Based on MAXAM's field engineer data","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"*Based on MAXAM's field engineer data","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8194-ad7f-cd02e27822fb","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-814c-b08a-ecac35715a01"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Taking the existing MS402 tread pattern, MAXAM’s engineers took the two existing straight lines and changed them into rounded arc. In addition, they also modified six pieces of small lugs into four bigger lugs for enhanced traction. To prevent stones on the road from trapping and resulting in deep cuts and separation, a stone ejector design was added at the area prone to stone trapping.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Taking the existing MS402 tread pattern, MAXAM’s engineers took the two existing straight lines and changed them into rounded arc. In addition, they also modified six pieces of small lugs into four bigger lugs for enhanced traction. To prevent stones on the road from trapping and resulting in deep cuts and separation, a stone ejector design was added at the area prone to stone trapping.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-818d-b710-e52f37fd5d46","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-814c-b08a-ecac35715a01"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"image","image":{"caption":[],"type":"external","external":{"url":"https://maxamtire.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/412-drawing.png"}},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8141-9c09-fcd05c116478","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-814c-b08a-ecac35715a01"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T21:58:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Some of the other features and benefits that MS412's users have stated include: ","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Some of the other features and benefits that MS412's users have stated include: ","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"de